    "description": "Postman collection for testing the rebuilt user-service registration, resume, login, and forgot PIN flow.\n\nImportant: OTP is normally printed in application logs by the sample implementation. Copy the OTP from logs and set collection variable `otpCode` before calling OTP verification/reset APIs.",
